wdi-AG.PRD.FOOD.XD.def: Food production index covers food crops that are considered edible and that contain nutrients. Coffee and tea are excluded because, although edible, they have no nutritive value.
wdi-AG.PRD.FOOD.XD.name: Food production index
wdi-AG.PRD.FOOD.XD.source: Food and Agriculture Organization, electronic files and web site.
